order border-white/10 text-white text-center py-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest group-hover:bg-electric-blue group-hover:border-electric-blue transition-all\">View Course Details</div></div></a><a class=\"group glass border border-white/5 hover:border-electric-blue/40 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col h-full overflow-hidden\" href=\"/training/business-digitalization\"><div class=\"bg-midnight-mid border-b border-electric-blue/20 p-8 relative\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-electric-blue/5 blur-3xl group-hover:bg-electric-blue/10 transition-colors\"></div><span class=\"inline-block bg-electric-blue/10 text-electric-blue text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold py-1 px-3 rounded-sm mb-4\">Enrolling Now</span><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors\">Transform Your Business Digitally</h3><p class=\"text-grey text-sm line-clamp-2\">Learn to digitize traditional businesses. E-commerce, digital payments, online presence, and automation for Nigerian businesses.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 flex-grow flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex gap-4 mb-6 pb-6 border-b border-white/5\"><div class=\"text-xs text-grey font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2\">⏱️ <!-- -->6 Weeks</div><div class=\"text-xs text-grey font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2\">💻 <!-- -->Online</div></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 mb-8 flex-grow\"><li class=\"text-sm text-cream flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1 text-xs\">✦</span><span>Digital Assessment</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-cream flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1 text-xs\">✦</span><span>Online Presence</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-cream flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1 text-xs\">✦</span><span>E-commerce</span></li><li class=\"text-sm text-cream flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-gold mt-1 text-xs\">✦</span><span>Digital Payments</span></li></ul><div class=\"mt-auto w-full border border-white/10 text-white text-center py-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest group-hover:bg-electric-blue group-hover:border-electric-blue transition-all\">View Course Details</div></div></a></div><div class=\"mt-32 p-12 bg-midnight-mid border border-white/5 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><p class=\"text-electric-blue text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold mb-4\">The Challenge</p><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">Most Tech Courses Teach Theory.<br/>We Teach <span class=\"text-electric-blue italic\">Execution.</span></h3><p class=\"text-grey leading-relaxed mb-8\">The Nigerian tech space is full of &quot;gurus&quot; selling outdated courses. When you graduate, you still don&#x27;t know how to land a client or deliver a professional project. We teach you the exact frameworks and code we use to deliver high-ticket projects to our clients.</p></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-midnight-mid border-t border-white/10 pt-20 pb-10\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 group\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative w-8 h-8 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"Hephzibah Media Logo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-contain group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2FHephzibah%20Media%20Logo.png